<H2><A NAME="LogEmail">Anonymous_LogEmail directive</A></H2>
<A
 HREF="directive-dict.html#Syntax"
 REL="Help"
><STRONG>Syntax:</STRONG></A> Anonymous_LogEmail on|off<BR>
<A
 HREF="directive-dict.html#Default"
